       </p>
      </div>
      <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA05d242n1-ptr" id="PJA05d242n1">1</a>
       <p>For a fuller itemization but still incomplete account, see <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Diary and Autobiography of John Adams&lt;/i&gt;, ed. L. H. Butterfield and others, Cambridge, 1961; 4 vols. ]">JA, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Diary and Autobiography</span></span>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-01-02-02-0007-0001-0001#ADMS-01-02-02-pb-0252" class="pageNo">2:252257</a> and notes there.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA05d242n2-ptr" id="PJA05d242n2">2</a>
       <p>For <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>s moving into the home of Rev. James Sproat, see same, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-01-02-02-0007-0003-0001" class="document">2:262</a>.</p>
      </div>
